latestPosts.caption:
1KG of shopping at 655 in Pondicherry?! 🤫😱

Imagine walking into a store and coming out with 1KG of clothes for just ₹655—yep, that’s around ₹150 per item! Tell me that’s not insane! 🤯

This is an export surplus hidden gem 👀 These are clothes originally made for big brands but never made it to retail—either due to excess production, minor defects, or order cancellations. Pretty much the same quality, but at prices that’ll make you do a double take! 🤭

You’ll find tshirts, jeans, joggers, hoodies, shorts, workout clothes, cute dresses, menswear and even kidswear!! Ngl some of it isn’t that amazing, but if you have the patience to dig through, you’ll find absolute gold!💰

And yes, I’ve shopped here before—past finds still going strong.

Drop a comment “location” and I’ll spill the tea ☕️📍 — this one’s too good to miss!
